    <headline>High forest fire danger, orange level, Outer parts of Sunnmøre and Romsdal, 2022-11-24T10:00:00+00:00, 2022-12-02T12:00:00+00:00</headline>
    <description>Due to lasting dry conditions for more than two weeks, there is now local high grass fire danger in areas free of snow. Valid until significant precipitation. </description>
    <instruction>Be very careful with open fire. Follow the instructions from the local authorities. Emergency services should assess a necessary level of alertness. </instruction>
